Description: Fast screenshots with annotations
 Tray-resident screenshot tool with a built-in annotation editor.
 Global hotkey opens a region selector across all monitors; nine annotation
 tools (pen, line, arrow, rectangle, ellipse, marker, text, numbered step,
 blur/pixelate); four colour palettes; save, copy, or pin to screen.
